WEBVTT

00:00.184 --> 00:02.890
This is the Bravia OLED...

00:03.227 --> 00:07.201
...and this is a unique execution of an OLED display...

00:07.374 --> 00:10.544
...that only Sony, that only Sony can really bring to life.

00:12.373 --> 00:16.559
OLED is designed to reproduce deep blacks in dark scenes.

00:17.101 --> 00:21.261
And when it's combined with our X1 Extreme processing technology,...

00:21.485 --> 00:23.686
...it renders every detail of an image...

00:23.886 --> 00:27.241
...regardless of any ambient darkness in the scene.

